						<description sparkle:format="plain-text">• Updated the design of the card cells
• Updated the layout of the board
• Added variable spacing of cards in a stack based on the available space
• Added a slight jitter to card stacks
• Added a Deck & Game Settings button in the titlebar (currently only allows changing the deck by right-clicking)

• Removed the confirmation dialog when starting a new game

• Fixed the incorrect positioning of cards in a stack after dropping them
• Fixed an issue that caused the app to quit unexpectedly when a font was not installed on the user's device
